               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Clotrimazole Cream USP, 1% is supplied in  30 g (NDC 68071-2469-3) tubes.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20200124"/>
               <component>
